1
00:00:22,026 --> 00:00:23,626
A friend?

2
00:00:23,626 --> 00:00:26,797
Can you explain again what you told me earlier?

3
00:00:27,465 --> 00:00:31,545
So there's this guy named Oh Beomseok. He's a student at Byeoksan High School.

4
00:00:31,545 --> 00:00:32,847
- Oh Beomseok.
- Right.

5
00:00:32,847 --> 00:00:35,616
He called me and said to come out, but when I went,

6
00:00:35,616 --> 00:00:38,442
- there were many others…
- Yeongi.

7
00:00:40,144 --> 00:00:42,212
Hey, are you all right?

8
00:00:44,549 --> 00:00:48,051
Are you okay? Where are the other students?

9
00:00:49,487 --> 00:00:51,722
I was there by myself.

10
00:00:53,424 --> 00:00:57,227
Hey, you can tell us the truth.

11
00:00:57,227 --> 00:00:58,896
Don't worry.

12
00:01:00,632 --> 00:01:02,640
I was there alone.

13
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:04,600
What the hell?

14
00:01:05,904 --> 00:01:10,616
Please. Don't speak about today's incident to Suho.

15
00:01:10,616 --> 00:01:12,309
What?

16
00:01:13,810 --> 00:01:15,240
[Happy Birthday]

17
00:01:15,246 --> 00:01:16,814
Hey, Yeon Sieun!

18
00:01:20,285 --> 00:01:21,952
Hey, Sieun!

19
00:02:06,764 --> 00:02:08,365
Hey, Beomseok.

20
00:02:12,337 --> 00:02:13,737
Yes?

21
00:02:14,472 --> 00:02:16,707
You need to stop this now.

22
00:02:18,343 --> 00:02:20,611
Don't bother Suho anymore.

23
00:02:52,770 --> 00:02:55,300
[Park Ji Hoon]

24
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:57,960
[Choi Hyeon Wook]

25
00:02:57,960 --> 00:03:00,540
[Hong Kyeong]

26
00:03:00,540 --> 00:03:02,560
[Lee Yeon]

27
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,650
[Shin Seung Ho]

28
00:03:04,650 --> 00:03:08,550
[WEAK HERO CLASS 1]
♫ The heart that you take out after passing ♫

29
00:03:08,550 --> 00:03:11,270
♫ It's an old regret ♫

30
00:03:11,270 --> 00:03:15,340
♫ It's already too late ♫

31
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:20,420
♫ Words I didn't want to hear ♫

32
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:23,390
♫ A face covered with a hand ♫

33
00:03:23,390 --> 00:03:27,940
♫ I didn't know I'd miss you ♫

34
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:40,120
♫ I regret it, let's not cry anymore ♫

35
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:52,610
♫ Sigh. Please don't hide ♫

36
00:03:56,510 --> 00:03:59,960
[Original: SeoPass - Kim Jin Seok "Weak Hero"]

37
00:04:02,714 --> 00:04:05,817
[Dividing a three-digit by a two-digit]

38
00:04:07,452 --> 00:04:11,332
Where were you, and what were you doing while Sieun was getting hurt?

39
00:04:11,332 --> 00:04:14,692
- I can't even ask that?
- You're not the only one who's busy.

40
00:04:14,692 --> 00:04:19,270
Do you think I just bum around at home while you go to your practices and competitions?

41
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:21,408
You said we'd raise him together.

42
00:04:21,408 --> 00:04:23,310
You said we'd get through this together.

43
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,945
We had him because you wanted…

44
00:04:24,945 --> 00:04:27,571
I didn't know anything back then!

45
00:04:29,207 --> 00:04:32,687
I thought kids grew by themselves. Who knew he'd be so sick all the time?

46
00:04:40,985 --> 00:04:44,454
Sieun.

47
00:04:46,891 --> 00:04:49,370
Sieun, please let me in.

48
00:04:49,370 --> 00:04:50,995
Let me talk to you.

49
00:04:50,995 --> 00:04:54,531
Sieun, could you please let us in? Please?

50
00:04:55,500 --> 00:05:00,437
Sieun, please let me in. Let me talk to you for a minute.

51
00:05:01,406 --> 00:05:03,373
Yeon Sieun.

52
00:05:03,373 --> 00:05:08,012
Daddy and Mommy weren't fighting. We were just talking. Sieun!

53
00:05:09,414 --> 00:05:13,617
- Sieun, Yeon Sieun.
- Hey, Sieun.

54
00:05:15,587 --> 00:05:17,187
Hey, Sieun.

55
00:05:26,631 --> 00:05:30,100
I'm telling you that it's okay. Tell me the truth.

56
00:05:30,969 --> 00:05:34,209
Was it the same guys as the ones who hurt your face last time?

57
00:05:35,373 --> 00:05:36,813
I'm telling you the truth.

58
00:05:36,813 --> 00:05:39,242
I fell down the stairs.

59
00:05:39,242 --> 00:05:41,578
I asked for the truth.

60
00:05:42,013 --> 00:05:43,814
Then, why were you even there?

61
00:05:45,350 --> 00:05:47,050
Just for no reason.

62
00:05:50,321 --> 00:05:54,190
When you get discharged, I'm transferring you to another school.

63
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:55,759
I don't want to.

64
00:05:55,759 --> 00:05:57,727
Are you serious?

65
00:05:57,727 --> 00:06:00,163
What is wrong with you?

66
00:06:00,163 --> 00:06:01,709
Don't you know how hard I'm working?

67
00:06:01,733 --> 00:06:04,568
- So you'd better listen to me.
- Dad.

68
00:06:07,705 --> 00:06:10,274
I've always wondered about this.

69
00:06:10,942 --> 00:06:14,311
Since when were you so interested in me?

70
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:16,880
What?

71
00:06:24,289 --> 00:06:25,889
Nothing.

72
00:07:15,473 --> 00:07:16,873
Yes?

73
00:07:18,610 --> 00:07:20,250
Mr. Beomseok is home right now.

74
00:07:20,250 --> 00:07:21,488
How did it go?

75
00:07:21,488 --> 00:07:23,312
I told the Seocho Police to hold their tongue.

76
00:07:23,312 --> 00:07:26,417
Same with the school. I spoke with the principal.

77
00:07:27,118 --> 00:07:30,664
Mrs. Oh went to Jeju Island, so stay home and watch him.

78
00:07:30,664 --> 00:07:33,257
We don't know what he'll do.

79
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:38,804
And look up some schools in the Philippines. We're sending him abroad.

80
00:07:38,804 --> 00:07:40,263
Yes, sir.

81
00:07:43,334 --> 00:07:45,202
How did you know?

82
00:07:48,940 --> 00:07:52,910
Mr. Park told me that you'd be in there.

83
00:07:53,611 --> 00:07:55,771
I mean, the incident that happened yesterday.

84
00:07:59,083 --> 00:08:01,283
I got a call from the police department.

85
00:08:01,853 --> 00:08:03,953
Yeon Sieun.

86
00:08:03,953 --> 00:08:08,458
He didn't want to press any charges. He said he was your friend.

87
00:08:12,330 --> 00:08:17,034
Why do you think the uprising happened? That is the important question.

88
00:08:17,569 --> 00:08:19,503
Hey, wake him up.

89
00:08:20,205 --> 00:08:22,405
- Wake up your classmates.
- Suho.

90
00:08:22,405 --> 00:08:24,240
Hey, Suho.

91
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:26,477
Where did we leave off?

92
00:08:28,045 --> 00:08:30,247
Why are you guys so quiet?

93
00:08:31,316 --> 00:08:33,517
Class rep, what page were we on?

94
00:08:33,518 --> 00:08:35,596
We were on page 100. The Japan-Korea Treaty of 1876.

95
00:08:35,596 --> 00:08:37,888
Is that so? Then…

96
00:08:39,190 --> 00:08:44,561
Go to page 109. Let's learn about the Donghak Peasant Revolution.

97
00:08:45,230 --> 00:08:51,202
Donghak Peasant Revolution. In order to learn about it, we must…

98
00:08:55,807 --> 00:08:57,909
[An Suho]

99
00:09:03,748 --> 00:09:05,159
[Why aren't you answering?]

100
00:09:05,159 --> 00:09:08,118
[I have some issues at home, so I can't go to school]

101
00:09:11,756 --> 00:09:16,126
Why didn't you come home last night? And you ignored all my calls.

102
00:09:16,126 --> 00:09:17,794
What about it?

103
00:09:20,565 --> 00:09:22,967
When is this birthday prank going to end?

104
00:09:22,967 --> 00:09:25,269
Is this a part of it? Is it?

105
00:09:26,070 --> 00:09:29,406
It's not fun anymore. Stop it.

106
00:09:30,441 --> 00:09:34,611
It's not a prank. I'm sorry about yesterday.

107
00:10:07,512 --> 00:10:09,781
[Final Exam: D-1]

108
00:10:09,781 --> 00:10:11,581
- Hey!
- Damn it.

109
00:10:12,383 --> 00:10:13,883
Let's go smoke.

110
00:10:27,632 --> 00:10:29,872
Why isn't Beomseok coming to school?

111
00:10:31,469 --> 00:10:33,269
I don't know.

112
00:10:33,269 --> 00:10:35,444
You haven't tried calling?

113
00:10:35,444 --> 00:10:37,574
You're his besties.

114
00:10:37,574 --> 00:10:40,477
His phone is off. Hey, do you know?

115
00:10:40,477 --> 00:10:42,656
Tell him to pay for the damages if you get hold of him.

116
00:10:42,656 --> 00:10:44,581
Okay, I will…

117
00:10:47,885 --> 00:10:49,285
Pardon?

118
00:10:50,521 --> 00:10:52,321
What damages?

119
00:10:56,494 --> 00:10:58,329
It's 800,000 won.

120
00:11:00,131 --> 00:11:02,733
If you don't pay me back, you're all dead.

121
00:11:05,436 --> 00:11:07,036
Answer me.

122
00:11:07,839 --> 00:11:09,239
Okay.

123
00:11:13,144 --> 00:11:16,046
[Jeongchan]

124
00:11:21,653 --> 00:11:22,863
The number you have called…

125
00:11:22,863 --> 00:11:26,422
Fuck! Beomseok. Answer me already.

126
00:11:26,422 --> 00:11:28,692
We still need to beat up An Suho. Damn it.

127
00:11:28,692 --> 00:11:31,486
Why isn't Yeon Sieun coming to school?

128
00:11:31,486 --> 00:11:33,597
What if he's really dead?

129
00:11:33,597 --> 00:11:37,900
- Yeongbin was too much the other day.
- Hey. Don't make it a big deal.

130
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:41,605
Then our teacher would've told us to go to his funeral.

131
00:12:08,533 --> 00:12:10,401
Please, stop!

132
00:12:11,369 --> 00:12:14,682
Oh Beomseok called you first, but you didn't answer.

133
00:12:14,682 --> 00:12:16,317
So we took that girl.

134
00:12:16,317 --> 00:12:18,041
To call you out.

135
00:12:18,543 --> 00:12:19,843
What?

136
00:12:19,843 --> 00:12:24,681
That girl who lives with you, but…

137
00:12:24,681 --> 00:12:27,518
but Yeon Sieun came instead of you.

138
00:12:36,594 --> 00:12:38,539
- So what happened?
- Then…

139
00:12:38,539 --> 00:12:42,775
Yeongbin has this friend, and Beomseok gave him money to beat you up.

140
00:12:44,135 --> 00:12:47,004
Beomseok did everything. We just stood next to him.

141
00:13:07,258 --> 00:13:08,658
What?

142
00:13:10,728 --> 00:13:12,863
Which hospital is Sieun in?

143
00:13:20,371 --> 00:13:22,272
He was discharged today.

144
00:13:24,676 --> 00:13:26,877
I'm sorry. It's all my fault.

145
00:13:32,784 --> 00:13:34,284
Hey!

146
00:13:41,959 --> 00:13:44,899
Sieun told me to keep it secret from you no matter what.

147
00:13:46,898 --> 00:13:48,878
Don't get into any trouble.

148
00:14:05,984 --> 00:14:07,784
Who is it?

149
00:14:09,254 --> 00:14:11,088
Delivery.

150
00:14:15,626 --> 00:14:17,594
Why are you here?

151
00:14:17,594 --> 00:14:22,399
What kind of question is that? I'm so thirsty. Give me a cup of water.

152
00:14:36,714 --> 00:14:38,114
Hey.

153
00:14:39,317 --> 00:14:41,217
How have you been?

154
00:14:43,521 --> 00:14:47,391
Good. What brings you here?

155
00:14:47,392 --> 00:14:50,661
I just stopped by on my way.

156
00:15:04,642 --> 00:15:06,242
Are you all right?

157
00:15:09,747 --> 00:15:11,247
With what?

158
00:15:18,223 --> 00:15:21,463
You're coming to school, right? The finals are tomorrow.

159
00:15:23,795 --> 00:15:27,264
Yes, I have to go.

160
00:15:27,832 --> 00:15:30,234
Okay. All right.

161
00:15:30,835 --> 00:15:32,535
See you tomorrow.

162
00:16:36,401 --> 00:16:38,936
- Is he in his room?
- Yes, he is.

163
00:16:40,872 --> 00:16:43,273
You crazy punk.

164
00:16:43,273 --> 00:16:45,376
You piece of trash.

165
00:16:46,211 --> 00:16:50,514
I told you not to embarrass me, didn't I?

166
00:16:50,514 --> 00:16:54,418
What the hell is your problem? What the hell is your freaking problem?!

167
00:16:54,418 --> 00:17:00,322
You little fucker, I told you to obey me and do only as I say!

168
00:17:00,322 --> 00:17:03,736
I told you to stay hidden. Was that so hard?

169
00:17:03,761 --> 00:17:06,774
Was that so freaking hard for you, you bastard?

170
00:17:06,774 --> 00:17:09,933
You useless piece of fucking trash!

171
00:17:09,933 --> 00:17:13,170
What am I to do with this fucker?

172
00:17:13,170 --> 00:17:17,775
I'm going to send you abroad.

173
00:17:17,775 --> 00:17:21,846
I don't care if you overdose on drugs. Do whatever you want.

174
00:17:22,981 --> 00:17:25,926
Just don't go around telling anyone that you're my son.

175
00:17:25,926 --> 00:17:27,718
Understand?

176
00:17:28,286 --> 00:17:31,989
Hey! Keep an eye on him at all times.

177
00:17:38,529 --> 00:17:41,198
I never asked you to adopt me.

178
00:18:00,718 --> 00:18:02,618
Mr. Beomseok.

179
00:18:02,620 --> 00:18:04,788
Let go of me. Fuck.

180
00:18:06,257 --> 00:18:08,192
Go to hell. Damn it.

181
00:18:14,999 --> 00:18:17,901
- Where to?
- Please just start driving.

182
00:18:34,919 --> 00:18:36,988
[Wednesday, November 13]

183
00:18:40,291 --> 00:18:43,695
[Missed Calls]

184
00:18:44,963 --> 00:18:48,499
[Message: Suho]

185
00:18:50,835 --> 00:18:53,871
[Answer before I kill all your friends]

186
00:19:01,512 --> 00:19:04,291
Hey, just a second.

187
00:19:04,291 --> 00:19:08,716
So call Beomseok and bring him here.

188
00:19:09,988 --> 00:19:14,858
I don't know where he is either. I really can't get hold of him.

189
00:19:21,032 --> 00:19:23,167
Then it's "an eye for an eye".

190
00:19:37,582 --> 00:19:41,185
[Beomseok]

191
00:19:47,358 --> 00:19:48,858
Where are you?

192
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:57,280
I asked a question, you bastard.

193
00:19:59,671 --> 00:20:01,171
Why?

194
00:20:01,940 --> 00:20:03,740
Oh Beomseok.

195
00:20:05,009 --> 00:20:06,944
Stop hiding from me.

196
00:20:23,361 --> 00:20:25,529
Damn it.

197
00:20:35,075 --> 00:20:39,410
[Oh Beomseok]

198
00:20:44,515 --> 00:20:46,015
Yeah, what?

199
00:20:50,622 --> 00:20:52,689
Let's go get An Suho.

200
00:20:53,725 --> 00:20:55,325
I'll pay you.

201
00:21:08,306 --> 00:21:12,042
[Boxing for middle and high schoolers, atheletes, personalized classes]

202
00:21:25,123 --> 00:21:26,523
Hello?

203
00:21:27,158 --> 00:21:28,558
Hey.

204
00:21:29,594 --> 00:21:32,029
Have you talked to Suho?

205
00:21:33,731 --> 00:21:37,301
Yeah. He came to see me this afternoon.

206
00:21:38,069 --> 00:21:41,205
He found out about what happened that day.

207
00:21:41,205 --> 00:21:42,672
What?

208
00:21:43,675 --> 00:21:47,175
He hasn't come to work yet, and he isn't answering his phone.

209
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:51,515
Did he say anything to you?

210
00:21:55,186 --> 00:22:00,086
He couldn't have gone to see Beomseok, could he?

211
00:22:01,559 --> 00:22:03,627
I'll try calling him.

212
00:22:25,183 --> 00:22:26,883
Are you serious?

213
00:22:28,620 --> 00:22:30,654
You crazy bastards.

214
00:22:30,654 --> 00:22:32,522
What is all this?

215
00:22:35,093 --> 00:22:36,793
Where's Oh Beomseok?

216
00:23:23,675 --> 00:23:25,475
Long time no see.

217
00:23:30,615 --> 00:23:33,550
If you were mad at me, you should've come to me.

218
00:23:33,550 --> 00:23:35,786
Why bother other people?

219
00:23:37,055 --> 00:23:39,156
They didn't do anything.

220
00:23:46,698 --> 00:23:48,498
Let me apologize.

221
00:23:53,271 --> 00:23:55,339
I hurt your feelings.

222
00:24:01,446 --> 00:24:03,747
Now that I've apologized,

223
00:24:05,583 --> 00:24:08,418
you need to apologize to Sieun and Yeongi.

224
00:24:11,089 --> 00:24:12,889
I don't want to.

225
00:24:13,992 --> 00:24:16,560
I'm not sorry about anything.

226
00:24:18,663 --> 00:24:20,563
Please, apologize.

227
00:24:25,069 --> 00:24:26,904
I said no.

228
00:24:32,377 --> 00:24:34,311
Then I should beat you.

229
00:24:35,246 --> 00:24:37,247
Until you come to your senses.

230
00:24:43,521 --> 00:24:45,421
Hey, An Suho.

231
00:24:48,259 --> 00:24:49,859
I see.

232
00:24:52,297 --> 00:24:54,197
Come up to the ring.

233
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:58,768
You're really paying him?

234
00:24:58,768 --> 00:25:00,871
To beat me up?

235
00:25:04,776 --> 00:25:07,578
You're so freaking pathetic.

236
00:25:13,685 --> 00:25:16,353
Give me a minute. Let me warm up.

237
00:25:18,456 --> 00:25:20,156
You bastard.

238
00:25:38,176 --> 00:25:40,244
So you've been keeping up.

239
00:25:40,244 --> 00:25:42,089
That's quite impressive.

240
00:25:42,089 --> 00:25:44,815
Remember I knocked you out last time?

241
00:25:46,951 --> 00:25:48,451
Come up here.

242
00:26:05,303 --> 00:26:08,482
Hey, guys. It's the match you've all been waiting for,

243
00:26:08,482 --> 00:26:10,885
Remember I said I was beaten up in middle school?

244
00:26:10,885 --> 00:26:15,779
Today, I'll be getting my revenge through a proper fight.

245
00:26:15,779 --> 00:26:17,280
Salute.

246
00:26:21,286 --> 00:26:22,262
Come on.

247
00:26:22,262 --> 00:26:24,221
Let's make it entertaining.

248
00:26:24,221 --> 00:26:25,522
All right?

249
00:26:28,226 --> 00:26:29,926
You freaking bastard.

250
00:26:42,307 --> 00:26:44,508
Damn it. That was so close.

251
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:50,591
You hurt your left leg, right?

252
00:26:50,591 --> 00:26:52,816
So what if I did, you bastard?

253
00:27:13,204 --> 00:27:14,849
You need to get your revenge!

254
00:27:14,849 --> 00:27:17,007
Go for his leg!

255
00:27:17,007 --> 00:27:19,576
- Okay!
- Yes! Good job!

256
00:27:23,748 --> 00:27:25,750
- Damn.
- That bastard.

257
00:27:26,517 --> 00:27:28,629
- You were lucky.
- Shut up, you punk!

258
00:27:28,629 --> 00:27:30,197
- Nice!
- That's it!

259
00:27:30,197 --> 00:27:32,022
- That bastard!
- Nice!

260
00:27:32,724 --> 00:27:33,801
- Get him!
- Beat him!

261
00:27:33,801 --> 00:27:34,902
- More!
- Yeah!

262
00:27:34,902 --> 00:27:36,527
That punk!

263
00:27:41,199 --> 00:27:42,700
This isn't good.

264
00:27:43,301 --> 00:27:45,001
Damn it.

265
00:27:49,641 --> 00:27:50,618
You fucker.

266
00:27:50,618 --> 00:27:51,719
Hey!

267
00:27:51,719 --> 00:27:53,644
Damn you!

268
